name: Who Lives Here?
tagline: A simple app to help find your friends when you're traveling.
body: Who Lives Here? is a project by [Jack Flintermann](@jflinter). It's open-source, so you can build it for yourself, or just get it from the [App Store](https://appsto.re/us/klJrY.i) (it's free, so that option is almost certainly easier.) I hope you like it!
